{"tid":458623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首宗個案！男子北上羅湖被截　4部iPX全沒收","createTime":"2017-11-05T05:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T23:36:58.000Z","uid":75211,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8137bb4c0ca57028d869d7cb8166b0d43ff208f8","tid":458623,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"美國蘋果公司10周年版手機iPhone X周五（3日）首日發售，深圳羅湖海關隨即查獲首宗違規攜帶iPhone X入境案。以64GB版本計算，4部手機估算值約34352元（港元‧下同）；若是256GB的話則約39552元。 <br />\n<br />\n據羅湖海關通報，周五下午約3時，一名身穿藍底白色條紋T恤的年輕男子，從香港經羅湖口岸入境深圳。負責檢查的關員透露，該名男子行李簡單，只背着一個中等大小的背囊，當關員示意他要接受檢查時，男子就有點呆了，「打開背包一看，裏面就是4部全新的iPhone X手機，其他甚麼都沒有」。目前海關已對該名涉案旅客立案調查。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/131428_4c796cfe7016e7c195afba15380dd95b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F131428_4c796cfe7016e7c195afba15380dd95b.jpg&h=9b4d1fd6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/131429_91a069a623ebd897d715817f6d0ea153.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F131429_91a069a623ebd897d715817f6d0ea153.jpg&h=3e536c2a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/131430_edb6b3f8fa37874efbe42afb6fd9a5ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F131430_edb6b3f8fa37874efbe42afb6fd9a5ab.jpg&h=02fe29f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ccacb9bb643cea634632e2ed75789d8937880d66","tid":458623,"uid":75211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20171103/mobile/bkncn-20171103163050059-1103_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171103%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20171103163050059-1103_05011_001.html&d=AVe2VvwzaJ11tKqN4%2Bn9uKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f678b29e\